title: Manzanar National Historic Site: Federal Register Announcements
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Management     Federal Register Announcements              Federal Register Announcements      The Federal Register is a weekly publication of the Federal Government. It contains announcement of public meetings, law and policy changes, and National Park Service rulemaking decisions.When Manzanar National Historic Site publishes announcements related to these topics in the Federal Register, we will post that information on this page.
